snippet.title: Master System Longplay [083] Michael Jackson's Moonwalker
snippet.description:
http://www.longplays.org

Played by MadMatty

This the version i layed alot all thoe years ago, and I can still remember where most of the pickups are.  Not a bad game and can be forgiven for not being like the arcade version.  I also quite liked the music in the game. -
